high_descs: Walk straight towards the table and turn left to face the small black table.
Pick up the white cup from the table.
Turn right and walk towards the fridge on your left.
Place the cup on the top shelf inside the fridge, let it cool, and take it back out.
Turn left and head towards the small black table on your left.
Place the cup back on the table.
anns.task_desc: Cool down the cup on the small black table.

high_descs: Move forward to the table across the room, turn right and go to the small black table.
Pick up the mug on the small black table.
Move to the fridge on the right.
Chill the mug in the fridge.
Bring the chilled mug back to the small black table on the left of the fridge.
Put the chilled mug on the small black table.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled mug on the small black table.

high_descs: Go to the rack at the end of the counter on the right past the sink.
Pick up the coffee cup on the rack.
Take the cup across the room to the fridge.
Cool off the coffee cup in the fridge.
Take the cold cup back to the rack at the end of the counter past the sink.
Set the cold cup down on the rack.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold coffee cup on the rack.

high_descs: Go to the other side of the kitchen and face right.
Take the gray coffee mug on the black table
Turn around to go to the black refrigerator.
Place the coffee mug inside the refrigerator to chill it and take it out.
Go back to the black table where you got the coffee mug.
Place the coffee back on the black table.
